activities: GQueues collects information from users that sign in to access the GQueues service.  Companies in the EU and/or Switzerland are able to access and install GQueues.  The information collected includes name, email, address, phone and industry.  This information is used to personalize the GQueues service and to categorize which countries and industries utilize GQueues.  Additionally, the gqueues.com website as well as the GQueues blog collect contact information (name, email) from users that wish to be notified of updates or request additional information about GQueues and its service.
eucountries: Austria, Belgium, Bulgaria, Croatia, Cyprus, Czech Republic, Denmark, Estonia, Finland, France, Germany, Greece, Hungary, Iceland, Ireland, Italy, Latvia, Liechtenstein, Lithuania, Luxembourg, Malta, Netherlands, Norway, Poland, Portugal, Romania, Slovakia, Slovenia, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland, United Kingdom
personaldata: Online data and offline data from visitors and customers. Manually processed data not covered.
